{"id":1499,"date":"2026-07-02T13:11:15","date_gmt":"2026-07-02T12:11:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/?page_id=1499"},"modified":"2026-07-09T12:19:04","modified_gmt":"2026-07-09T11:19:04","slug":"collaborative-robotic-assembly-workstation","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/collaborative-robotic-assembly-workstation\/","title":{"rendered":"Collaborative Robotic Assembly Workstation"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1499\" class=\"elementor elementor-1499\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c04353f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c04353f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44a15cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"44a15cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/robotic_projects\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">\u2190 Back to Robotics Projects<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cca06c6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"cca06c6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c075882 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c075882\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Collaborative Robotic Assembly Workstation<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b553f8 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0b553f8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83d3773 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"83d3773\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8830cfe e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8830cfe\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67b47c3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"67b47c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Cobot_robodk-rpyug2kew2lvuscjxohubtg16oww6va32yio1mvuv4.png\" title=\"cobot robodk\" alt=\"cobot robodk\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3e6877 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c3e6877\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f3b9aa1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f3b9aa1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32ccf86 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"32ccf86\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"692\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Doosan-1.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1719\" alt=\"doosan\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Doosan-1.png 692w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Doosan-1-203x300.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 692px) 100vw, 692px\"  title=\"Collaborative Robotic Assembly Workstation\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b934d37 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b934d37\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7b51ca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d7b51ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The objective of this project was to design a collaborative assembly workstation where a human operator and a Doosan M0609 cobot work simultaneously on assembling an electronic enclosure.<\/p><p>The project focused on optimising task allocation, workstation ergonomics and robot programming while ensuring safe human\u2013robot collaboration. The workflow was first developed and validated in RobotDK before being adapted to the real robotic workstation.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1bffad e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e1bffad\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0c5f90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f0c5f90\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Project Information<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9e627db e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9e627db\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-762d9bf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"762d9bf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Duration<\/strong><\/p><p>September \u2013 December 2025<\/p><p><strong>Team<\/strong><\/p><p>2 students<\/p><p><strong>Role<\/strong><\/p><p>Collaborative Robotics \u2022 Robot Programming \u2022 Workstation Design<\/p><p><strong>Technologies<\/strong><\/p><p>RobotDK \u2022 Doosan M0609 \u2022 Fusion 360 \u2022 Dart Teach Pendant<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-41411e0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"41411e0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Features<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2853ac1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2853ac1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Workstation Design<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Designed the collaborative workstation layout.<\/li><li>Optimised component placement to minimise operator movement.<\/li><li>Analysed cycle times and task sequencing.<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Robot Programming<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Programmed assembly operations in RobotDK.<\/li><li>Developed modular programs for each assembly step.<\/li><li>Implemented tool-change and operator interaction routines.<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Simulation &amp; Validation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Created the complete RobotDK simulation.<\/li><li>Designed simplified CAD models of missing components in Fusion 360.<\/li><li>Validated the assembly sequence on the real Doosan cobot.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b64050 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0b64050\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Designing a Collaborative Workflow<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d8f0cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1d8f0cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Rather than assigning all tasks to the robot, the assembly process was divided according to the strengths of both the human operator and the cobot.<\/p><p>The robot performed repetitive and ergonomically demanding operations such as screwdriving and part handling, while the operator completed tasks requiring dexterity, including installing seals and connecting the electronic board.<\/p><p>This approach reduced operator fatigue while maintaining an efficient production cycle. The task allocation was planned to enable parallel work, reducing the estimated cycle time to approximately <strong>19 seconds per assembly<\/strong>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2113825 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2113825\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Robot Simulation<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59a4ed2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"59a4ed2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A complete digital workstation was developed in RobotDK before testing on the physical robot.<\/p><p>The simulation included:<\/p><ul><li>Robot programming<\/li><li>Tool changing<\/li><li>Screw feeder<\/li><li>Vacuum gripper<\/li><li>Assembly sequence<\/li><li>Safety pauses for operator interaction<\/li><\/ul><p>To improve the realism of the simulation, simplified CAD models of the enclosure, loudspeaker and PCB were created in Fusion 360 and imported into RobotDK.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4efc64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a4efc64\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Human\u2013Robot Interaction<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d929bca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d929bca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>One of the main objectives was ensuring safe collaboration between the operator and the robot.<\/p><p>Whenever manual intervention was required, the robot paused automatically until the operator confirmed that the workspace was clear.<\/p><p>During testing, this confirmation was implemented using pop-up messages on the teach pendant, while future improvements would replace these with a dedicated push button or foot pedal for a smoother workflow.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24a5b2d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"24a5b2d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Testing on the Real Robot<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a47a977 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a47a977\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>After validating the process in RobotDK, the assembly sequence was transferred to the Doosan M0609 collaborative robot.<\/p><p>Although the available lab time limited the implementation, the project demonstrated the transition from simulation to a real collaborative robotic cell and highlighted the practical differences between virtual programming and real-world deployment.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9ade06a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9ade06a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Results<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7dd7b90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7dd7b90\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The project successfully demonstrated:<\/p><p>\u2714 Collaborative human\u2013robot assembly<\/p><p>\u2714 RobotDK simulation of a complete workstation<\/p><p>\u2714 Task optimisation through parallel operations<\/p><p>\u2714 Validation on a real Doosan collaborative robot<\/p><p>\u2714 Modular robot programming<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e57c6a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e57c6a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What I Learned<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ff425f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6ff425f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This project gave me practical experience in designing collaborative robotic workstations, balancing productivity with operator safety and ergonomics.<\/p><p>Beyond learning RobotDK and Doosan robot programming, I gained a deeper understanding of workflow optimisation, human\u2013robot interaction and the challenges involved in transferring robotic applications from simulation to real industrial equipment.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u2190 Back to Robotics Projects Collaborative Robotic Assembly Workstation The objective of this project was to design a collaborative assembly workstation where a human operator and a Doosan M0609 cobot work simultaneously on assembling an electronic enclosure. The project focused on optimising task allocation, workstation ergonomics and robot programming while ensuring safe human\u2013robot collaboration. The [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"disabled","footer-sml-layout":"","ast-disable-related-posts":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"default","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"var(--ast-global-color-4)","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""},"tablet":{"background-color":"","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media"